data.description: Experience the allure of this stunning one-story home boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a versatile flex space. Laminate flooring graces the entire home, creating a seamless flow, while an abundance of natural light fills the open and functional layout. The kitchen is a chef's dream with elegant white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a spacious island perfect for entertaining. The flex room features beautiful wood sliding doors and a captivating accent wall, offering possibilities as an office, media room, or additional bedroom. The primary bedroom, secluded from the others, is airy and inviting, with an ensuite that includes dual sinks, a soaking tub, and a separate glass walk-in shower. Step outside to a backyard paradise featuring xeriscaped landscaping with turf and rock, a covered patio, flatwork fire pit with wooden chairs, and an outdoor TV-all included! Don't miss your chance to own this remarkable home where comfort and style meet.
